OL,3,CParty leaders start campaign push
OL,4,Cahead of Holyrood vote
OL,6,FScotland's party leaders are
OL,7,Fkickstarting their Holyrood election
OL,8,Fcampaigns as the race to become the
OL,9,Fnext first minister gets officially
OL,10,Funder way.
OL,12,FWith the Scottish Parliament having
OL,13,Ffinished on Wednesday, five of the
OL,14,Fmain parties standing in the election
OL,15,Fare holding launch events on Thursday.
OL,17,FWith six weeks to go until polling
OL,18,Fday, the contest is now fully under
OL,19,Fway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
