OL,3,CParty leaders start campaign push
OL,4,Cahead of Holyrood vote
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney will
OL,7,Fformally start the SNP's election
OL,8,Fcampaign at an event in Glasgow ` with
OL,9,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar and
OL,10,FScottish Conservative leader Russell
OL,11,FFindlay also marking the occasion.
OL,13,FScottish Green co-leaders Ross Greer
OL,14,Fand Gillian Mackay will also be out on
OL,15,Fthe campaign trail, along with Alex
OL,16,FCole-Hamilton of the Scottish Liberal
OL,17,FDemocrats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
