OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774505051
OL,3,CParty leaders start campaign push
OL,4,Cahead of Holyrood vote
OL,6,FThere is no event planned by Reform UK
OL,7,F` despite some polls suggesting Nigel
OL,8,FFarage's party could come second
OL,9,Foverall in the May 7 election.
OL,11,FHowever, the campaign gets under way
OL,12,Fwith the Reform UK Scotland leader
OL,13,Fhaving been forced to apologise for a
OL,14,Fhomophobic joke he made in 2018.
OL,16,FMr Swinney insisted that Reform could
OL,17,Fbe "locked out of power" if the SNP
OL,18,F"win big" with a majority in the
OL,19,FScottish Parliament.
OL,26,@yD@DOUyD@XO]zD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774505051
OL,3,CParty leaders start campaign push
OL,4,Cahead of Holyrood vote
OL,6,FHe has already set the SNP the goal of
OL,7,Fwinning an overall majority at
OL,8,FHolyrood in a bid to force a second
OL,9,Freferendum on independence.
OL,11,FBut Mr Swinney said such a result also
OL,12,F"locks Nigel Farage out of any
OL,13,Finfluence in Scotland's Parliament".
OL,15,FHe also told how an "historic
OL,16,Fmajority" for the SNP after May 7
OL,17,F"unlocks the potential for truly
OL,18,Ftransformational change with
OL,19,Findependence".
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@cO]wD@UOUxD@IO]yD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
