OL,3,CParty leaders start campaign push
OL,4,Cahead of Holyrood vote
OL,6,FScottish Liberal Democrat leader Alex
OL,7,FCole-Hamilton said he was "bursting
OL,8,Fwith excitement" for the election
OL,9,Fcampaign.
OL,11,FHe said: "I will be travelling all
OL,12,Fover our country letting people know
OL,13,Fthat the Liberal Democrats are winning
OL,14,Fagain, with more councillors, a record
OL,15,Fnumber of MPs and more to come."
OL,17,FHe will launch his party's campaign in
OL,18,Fthe Edinburgh Northern constituency,
OL,19,Fsaying Lib Dems are "on the verge" of
OL,20,Fwinning the seat from the SNP.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@PO]sD@JOUwD@`O]{D@UOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
