OL,3,CParty leaders start campaign push
OL,4,Cahead of Holyrood vote
OL,6,F"Our victories can deny them the
OL,7,Fparliamentary majority that John
OL,8,FSwinney craves," Mr Cole-Hamilton said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]
